    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "S03_left-detail",
      "x": 24,
      "y": 1630,
      "width": 373,
      "height": 126,
      "text": "📌 掌握的核心技能\n① config.yaml 三层结构（project / rules / context）\n② CLAUDE.md 分阶段交互防止 AI 乱跑\n③ Delta Spec 增量式更新，只写变化\n④ verify 三维验证：ops + spec + visual\n⑤ GitHub Pages 一键部署前端项目\n\n🎯 工具：openspec · 纯前端 React · Core Profile",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#444444",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "version": 2,
      "versionNonce": 943476880,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "seed": 3028,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": "S03_frame1",
      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776066468383,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "📌 掌握的核心技能\n① config.yaml 三层结构（project / rules / context）\n② CLAUDE.md 分阶段交互防止 AI 乱跑\n③ Delta Spec 增量式更新，只写变化\n④ verify 三维验证：ops + spec + visual\n⑤ GitHub Pages 一键部署前端项目\n\n🎯 工具：openspec · 纯前端 React · Core Profile",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "index": "b0C"
    },
