      "updated": 1776223325163,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "① openspec new change        →  写 proposal.md\n② openspec status --json     →  获取 Artifact Graph 构建顺序\n③ openspec instructions <id> →  逐个生成制品\n④ 制品全部生成完毕\n\nArtifact Graph 是 DAG（有向无环图）\n内部用 Kahn 算法做拓扑排序",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "① openspec new change        →  写 proposal.md\n② openspec status --json     →  获取 Artifact Graph 构建顺序\n③ openspec instructions <id> →  逐个生成制品\n④ 制品全部生成完毕\n\nArtifact Graph 是 DAG（有向无环图）\n内部用 Kahn 算法做拓扑排序",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "index": "b53"
    },
