      "updated": 1776223427213,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "💡 顺序必须：RENAMED 先执行使后续可引用新名；REMOVED 在 MODIFIED 前，防止修改即将删除的需求",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "baseline": 8,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "💡 顺序必须：RENAMED 先执行使后续可引用新名；REMOVED 在 MODIFIED 前，防止修改即将删除的需求",
