    {
      "id": "S20_el_txt_box_renamed",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 40.95477969425997,
      "y": 16787.896426401996,
      "width": 378,
      "height": 206,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e40af",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": "S20_frm_s20",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1060,
      "version": 662,
      "versionNonce": 50025824,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776223427213,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "✏️  RENAMED 操作详解\n\n格式：## RENAMED Requirements\nFROM: R-AUTH-PASSWORD-CHECK\n  TO: R-AUTH-CREDENTIAL-VALIDATION\n\n场景：密码检查 → 凭证验证\n（范围扩大，包含 OAuth）\n\n同时改名 + 改内容\n= RENAMED + MODIFIED 两步",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 9,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "✏️  RENAMED 操作详解\n\n格式：## RENAMED Requirements\nFROM: R-AUTH-PASSWORD-CHECK\n  TO: R-AUTH-CREDENTIAL-VALIDATION\n\n场景：密码检查 → 凭证验证\n（范围扩大，包含 OAuth）\n\n同时改名 + 改内容\n= RENAMED + MODIFIED 两步",
      "lineHeight": 1.5,
      "index": "bBH",
      "autoResize": true
    },
    {
      "id": "S20_el_txt_box_safety",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 457.6243979950883,
      "y": 16789.763185233216,
      "width": 394,
      "height": 206,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#4c1d95",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": "S20_frm_s20",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1061,
      "version": 678,
      "versionNonce": 665430368,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776223427213,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "🛡️  三重冲突检测\n\n① Orphaned MODIFIED\n   目标需求不存在 → 中止\n② Orphaned RENAMED\n   旧名不存在 → 中止\n③ Invalid Delta Format\n   缺标准 header → 失败\n\n✓ 验证失败不产生半写入状态",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 9,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "🛡️  三重冲突检测\n\n① Orphaned MODIFIED\n   目标需求不存在 → 中止\n② Orphaned RENAMED\n   旧名不存在 → 中止\n③ Invalid Delta Format\n   缺标准 header → 失败\n\n✓ 验证失败不产生半写入状态",
      "lineHeight": 1.5,
      "index": "bBI",
      "autoResize": true
    },
