    {
      "id": "S24_text-quote",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 57.05386421217463,
      "y": 19829.268911739608,
      "width": 840,
      "height": 18,
      "angle": 0,
      "text": "💬  Thoughtworks 技术总监：\"Spec drift 和 hallucination 本质上难以避免，我们仍然需要高确定性的 CI/CD 实践\"",
