      "type": "text",
      "x": 492.05386421217463,
      "y": 19877.268911739608,
      "width": 408,
      "height": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "text": "⚠️  Spec 漂移警告\n直接改代码 → spec 与代码漂移，目前无自动检测\n纪律：代码改了 → spec 也要改\n不能依赖 AI 自动同步！",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#991b1b",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
